545
00:48:00,495 --> 00:48:08,161
Thank you, Mr. President, and I'm honored tonight to offer this long-awaited resolution regarding

546
00:48:09,547 --> 00:48:11,088
charter review within our community.

547
00:48:11,849 --> 00:48:23,159
