571
00:51:33,508 --> 00:51:37,951
So I'm glad to see there's some movement now.

572
00:51:38,691 --> 00:51:41,973
Like I said, this is just the first step in a process.

573
00:51:42,774 --> 00:51:49,338
And I want to thank Solicitor Rumley for his due diligence on checking whether or not

574
00:51:50,073 --> 00:52:00,121
we could use a federal state and federal election to put city names on for a charter review commission, which he was told that we can do so.

575
00:52:00,561 --> 00:52:02,362
So we're able to do that this November.

576
00:52:03,323 --> 00:52:16,553
And I want to thank all the residents over the past probably four or five years now that have gone out, got signatures, gone out, had public meetings, gone out and promoted

577
00:52:17,818 --> 00:52:22,060
a review of a charter that hasn't been looked at in 29 years.

578
00:52:23,100 --> 00:52:30,923
Any business operating under a business plan that hasn't reviewed their business plan in 29 years, it's safe to say they would no longer be in business.

579
00:52:31,564 --> 00:52:32,984
And the City of Meffitt is no different.

580
00:52:33,825 --> 00:52:40,047
This charter is an important document in our city that dictates how government should operate.

581
00:52:40,527 --> 00:52:44,929
And at the very least, it deserves to be scrutinized

582
00:52:45,683 --> 00:52:49,105
and to allow residents of this community to give input.

583
00:52:49,786 --> 00:52:53,989
