01:28:14,369 --> 01:28:15,970
Maybe the things aren't going to go together.

944
01:28:16,391 --> 01:28:19,073
And they're just one will pass and one won't pass.

945
01:28:19,333 --> 01:28:21,454
And it won't change anything for the better.

946
01:28:21,855 --> 01:28:23,856
Maybe things don't need to be changed that much.

947
01:28:25,177 --> 01:28:35,024
I just don't think we should handcuff this group in any way, because we want this charter to be really looked at, because we want our city to be as great as it can be.

948
01:28:36,345 --> 01:28:38,547
But thank you for putting on this resolution.

949
01:28:39,147 --> 01:28:39,587
Thank you.

