01:28:44,691 --> 01:28:46,832
I'm Rob Capucci of 71 Evans Street.

955
01:28:48,419 --> 01:28:51,321
Thank you very much, Councilman Marks, for bringing this up.

956
01:28:52,601 --> 01:28:55,003
Always at your best and doing your due diligence.

957
01:28:55,483 --> 01:28:56,163
Love to see it.

958
01:28:56,623 --> 01:29:02,586
As you know, Dr. Starella and I tried to get the signatures for this about four or five years ago.

959
01:29:03,207 --> 01:29:09,630
And then another group led by a former mayor candidate, Anthony D'Antonio, tried as well.

960
01:29:10,110 --> 01:29:14,212
And now I'm glad to see that there's a third group trying to get this underway.

