01:30:19,821 --> 01:30:22,123
So I'm going to speak as plain as I can.

972
01:30:22,783 --> 01:30:26,746
This city has all of its power centered in the mayor's office.

973
01:30:27,487 --> 01:30:31,010
The city council's ultimate power basically is to cut the budget.

974
01:30:33,372 --> 01:30:35,673
