979
01:30:49,704 --> 01:30:53,586
I spent $94.50 in my campaign in 2013.

980
01:30:55,007 --> 01:31:00,030
I didn't ask for any money because I knew the special interest groups wouldn't support the kind of initiatives.

981
01:31:00,710 --> 01:31:05,713
This is it, folks, people watching, people listening tonight, this is the way to get

