993
01:31:45,822 --> 01:31:46,722
No question about it.

994
01:31:47,102 --> 01:31:47,802
Long overdue.

995
01:31:48,362 --> 01:31:50,943
Serious changes have to be made in the city of Medford.

996
01:31:51,283 --> 01:31:59,325
