2093
02:56:06,902 --> 02:56:18,607
Other than that, I know that if we can, I also want to make sure that we have that copy from the superintendent that he mentioned that will be done the first meeting of March in the school committee.

2094
02:56:18,627 --> 02:56:19,527
So thank you.

2095
02:56:19,647 --> 02:56:20,867
Thank you.

2096
02:56:21,128 --> 02:56:24,169
On the motion that we send this to the superintendent.

2097
02:56:24,189 --> 02:56:29,811
Mr. President, my name is Robert Penta, Zero Summit Road, former member of this body.

2098
02:56:29,991 --> 02:56:35,173
Last Tuesday night, along with myself and other taxpayers who came up before this podium,

2099
02:56:35,678 --> 02:56:54,228
The resolution that was introduced by Councilor Langel-Kern found itself in a libelous rebuttal by our superintendent, Mr. Belson, where he not only attacked Councilor Langel-Kern, Councilor Marks, myself, and resident citizens who came before this podium to express their freedom of speech rights,

2100
02:56:54,820 --> 02:56:58,183
as it relates to what's going on at Medford High School regarding a bomb threat.

2101
02:56:58,724 --> 02:57:08,153
As Councilor Lungo-Kern just alluded to, when a bomb threat takes place between 8 and 9 in the morning and parents aren't told until around 6 o'clock at night, that's an 8 to 9 hour spread.

2102
02:57:08,673 --> 02:57:10,955
The lack of communication was huge there.

2103
02:57:11,576 --> 02:57:13,858
And we were led to believe that protocols were in place.

2104
02:57:14,398 --> 02:57:17,081
And I think it was you, Councilor Scalpelli, along with Councilor Falco,

2105
02:57:17,421 --> 02:57:24,524
who indicated that you worked on a protocol procedure, and you were going to check it out the next night to make sure and to ensure the protocol was kept.

2106
02:57:25,004 --> 02:57:31,006
Now we're finding out that something is being manufactured, and it'll be ready sometime in March as it relates to what's going on.

2107
02:57:31,807 --> 02:57:41,911
The interesting part about that, in his libelous commentary that he wrote, he indicated that we were instilling fear within this community because we were here talking about this bomb that took place.

2108
02:57:42,411 --> 02:57:45,552
And I think it was Mr. Candy, in his comment in return,

2109
02:57:46,013 --> 02:57:50,596
for which he's re-quoted, he stated, you create fear when you don't inform the people.

2110
02:57:51,036 --> 02:57:51,797
And that's what happened.

2111
02:57:51,817 --> 02:57:54,339
They didn't get informed for almost eight to nine hours.

2112
02:57:55,059 --> 02:57:56,000
There wasn't a lockdown.

2113
02:57:56,040 --> 02:57:56,680
There was nothing.

2114
02:57:57,101 --> 02:58:04,926
No student, no teacher knew that there was a bomb threat that took place in that school, whether it was high level, low level, or big level, for whatever it might be.

2115
02:58:07,067 --> 02:58:09,969
You know, the same situation took place at Everett last week.

2116
02:58:10,770 --> 02:58:13,872
And the same problem existed, a lack of communication,

2117
02:58:14,248 --> 02:58:16,648
between the school administration to the parents.

2118
02:58:17,569 --> 02:58:21,869
And because of that, you just can't do that.

2119
02:58:22,730 --> 02:58:29,011
The superintendent should not be the sole provider of alleging that he can take care of the kids in that school.

2120
02:58:29,911 --> 02:58:33,372
You can't relay that commentary back to every single parent in that school.

2121
02:58:34,512 --> 02:58:36,052
That's not right, it's not fair.

2122
02:58:36,072 --> 02:58:40,713
If it was his kids or your children, it'd be a different story.

2123
02:58:42,044 --> 02:58:52,128
And the irony to this whole classic event was on the next night, up at the high school, in the library, a meeting on safety at Medford High School.

2124
02:58:53,789 --> 02:59:03,633
Well, if anyone went up there, you could walk into the building, no security guard, you could walk down the corridor to the library, no security guard, walk into the library.

2125
02:59:05,214 --> 02:59:07,135
What do you see, a police officer inside the library?

2126
02:59:07,468 --> 02:59:09,991
but no one at the front door, and nobody in the hallway.

2127
02:59:10,191 --> 02:59:15,536
And it's just as Councilor Marks alluded to, anybody could have walked into that building, put anything in that building at any time.

2128
02:59:15,816 --> 02:59:17,899
That's not instilling fear, that's the facts.

2129
02:59:18,179 --> 02:59:21,002
That's the hot, cold facts of what we're talking about.

2130
02:59:21,222 --> 02:59:24,125
And when you cut 80% of your security budget in the school department,

2131
02:59:24,685 --> 02:59:26,948
Over the past five or six years, that's what you get.

2132
02:59:27,468 --> 02:59:28,749
An insecure situation.

2133
02:59:29,030 --> 02:59:30,311
That's not instilling fear.

2134
02:59:30,611 --> 02:59:34,955
That's telling you you need to get your act together and protect those children up at that school.

2135
02:59:35,155 --> 02:59:36,196
Because that's what it's all about.

2136
02:59:36,236 --> 02:59:39,980
That's their responsibility as a school committee and as a superintendent.

2137
02:59:41,373 --> 02:59:43,455
That's a damn shame that that even took place.

2138
02:59:44,116 --> 02:59:51,064
And it's a shame that you're now hearing that you're going to get something that Councilor Alongo-Kern has alluded to, you want a copy of it when it comes out.

2139
02:59:51,685 --> 02:59:54,829
So apparently there wasn't any problem, I mean, any protocol.

2140
02:59:55,269 --> 02:59:57,512
There wasn't any management technique to take place.

2141
02:59:58,874 --> 03:00:00,856
And as of yesterday, from what I understand,

2142
03:00:01,232 --> 03:00:09,194
from speaking to some of the students and a few of the teachers, they still weren't aware until many days after the fact that a bomb threat had taken place in that building.

2143
03:00:09,794 --> 03:00:12,575
That is absolutely not fair and not right.

2144
03:00:13,295 --> 03:00:14,116
Absolutely not.

2145
03:00:14,296 --> 03:00:22,418
And I think it needs to be understood what a lockdown is as compared to what an evacuation is, as compared to a low level, a high level, and what a risk might be.

2146
03:00:23,278 --> 03:00:25,859
A teacher's not going to be Houdini to try to figure this out.

2147
03:00:26,019 --> 03:00:29,940
And apparently, a parent isn't, especially if they're not even notified.

2148
03:00:31,020 --> 03:00:54,037
Yes, I will stand here and I say I resent the libelous comment made by the superintendent of schools who said because I came up here, and you, Councilor Lungo-Kern, and you, Councilor Marks, and you, the citizens of this city, came up here to talk about a most egregious situation that's taking place in our city, and that's a lack of public safety and the communication to a parent if, in fact, public safety is challenged.

2149
03:00:54,617 --> 03:01:03,322
You, Mr. Superintendent, you should be ashamed of yourself for writing that commentary and you should probably resign because of what you said and what you wrote.

2150
03:01:04,043 --> 03:01:04,983
How dare you?

2151
03:01:05,263 --> 03:01:14,349
How dare you insinuate that anyone who comes for a podium and expresses their opinion is causing fear when in fact they were representing facts.

2152
03:01:14,869 --> 03:01:16,110
F-A-C-T-S.

2153
03:01:16,470 --> 03:01:19,672
Facts that took place under your watch, Mr. Superintendent.

2154
03:01:20,653 --> 03:01:23,154
Mr. President, I thank you for allowing me to make my comment.

2155
03:01:23,805 --> 03:01:26,106
Thank you.

2156
03:01:26,787 --> 03:01:39,133
Just to be clear, Mr. President, the, the comment that was made was to get the information that was going to be presented the following evening to see what protocol was put in place.

2157
03:01:39,754 --> 03:01:51,000
Now there was protocol in place that as a school team member, we reviewed, but at the time where the comment was mentioned, not talking to the superintendent will understand the protocol they followed.

2158
03:01:51,320 --> 03:01:52,821
We wouldn't know that to the following evening.

2159
03:01:52,861 --> 03:01:53,061
That's,

2160
03:01:53,491 --> 03:01:57,394
That's what I believe my fellow councilors, Mr. Falcon and myself, were alluding to.

2161
03:01:58,495 --> 03:01:58,856
Thank you.

2162
03:01:59,056 --> 03:01:59,336
Thank you.

2163
03:01:59,356 --> 03:02:02,759
Name and address of the record.

2164
03:02:03,219 --> 03:02:04,300
Thank you, Mr. President.

2165
03:02:04,641 --> 03:02:06,802
Robert Cappucci of 71 Evans Street.

2166
03:02:08,264 --> 03:02:11,026
Thank you, Councilor Longo Kern, for bringing this up.

2167
03:02:11,586 --> 03:02:18,873
And I have to second and echo the sentiments of the previous speaker, Mr. Robert Penter.

2168
03:02:22,530 --> 03:02:45,542
public official that's appointed to be getting the kind of money he's making a year on taxpayer dollars, to put out a letter like that that accuses, by name, private citizens of using inflammatory speech, was, I think, the exact word that he used, it's reprehensible.

2169
03:02:45,882 --> 03:02:50,925
We're talking earlier about the Charter Review and getting signatures and having an open podium.

2170
03:02:52,277 --> 03:02:53,878
This is all part of a free country.

2171
03:02:54,358 --> 03:03:06,205
Using words like that from the superintendent of schools of all people against private citizens, talking about instilling fear, that might scare people away from this podium, which might be the objective.

2172
03:03:06,566 --> 03:03:08,487
I'm not saying it is, but it might be.

2173
03:03:08,987 --> 03:03:10,168
And that's unconscionable.

2174
03:03:10,508 --> 03:03:14,130
That, to me, instills a lot of passion.

2175
03:03:14,930 --> 03:03:16,091
We live in a free country.

2176
03:03:16,151 --> 03:03:17,412
It comes with responsibility.

2177
03:03:17,765 --> 03:03:22,467
can't run in here and scream fire and not have consequences of that.

2178
03:03:22,707 --> 03:03:38,472
But this city council last Tuesday night had a very good resolution brought forth that was excellent for this forum, since it's this city council that decides the budget for the protocols to be made by the superintendent and the school committee.

2179
03:03:39,400 --> 03:03:49,945
I am beside myself when I comprehend this letter put out by the superintendent of schools that would frighten people away from this podium.

2180
03:03:50,185 --> 03:03:51,726
That's not what this country is all about.

2181
03:03:52,146 --> 03:03:57,329
And he really should either consider retiring or the mayor should consider replacing them.

2182
03:03:59,229 --> 03:04:08,834
Because this, I think, is something that could be the grounds for a recall vote of the administration if action isn't taken.

2183
03:04:09,418 --> 03:04:10,079
on this letter.

2184
03:04:10,739 --> 03:04:16,423
I wish he would apologize to the citizens he named specifically and to the citizens of Medford.

2185
03:04:16,483 --> 03:04:17,464
Thank you, Mr. President.

2186
03:04:19,946 --> 03:04:20,946
Name and address of the record, sir.

2187
03:04:21,207 --> 03:04:21,747
Good evening.

2188
03:04:21,787 --> 03:04:23,468
Joe Villione, 59 Garfield Ave.

2189
03:04:25,350 --> 03:04:27,351
Superintendent named me in the letter.

2190
03:04:28,072 --> 03:04:31,374
I didn't realize I had the power of a mayor or a city council or a school committee person.

2191
03:04:31,394 --> 03:04:32,615
I didn't realize I was that big in this.

2192
03:04:32,815 --> 03:04:38,519
I thought I was just a little guy, but Superintendent Belson, I went to the school that evening.

2193
03:04:39,028 --> 03:04:41,892
And there's a woman behind me, and I turned to her and I said, do you see security?

2194
03:04:41,952 --> 03:04:44,396
And she was in a rage over no security.

2195
03:04:44,777 --> 03:04:51,206
So I took out the iPhone and I have security desk, and you can see it up on YouTube, empty, empty.

2196
03:04:51,547 --> 03:04:52,408
Counselor Penta's right.

2197
03:04:53,592 --> 03:04:57,754
The one policeman there was Chief Sacco, and he was busy, engaged in the conversation.

2198
03:04:58,094 --> 03:05:00,475
So he wasn't in a position to help us.

2199
03:05:01,255 --> 03:05:04,577
We had a police officer sitting there with Roy Bellson, our mayor.

2200
03:05:04,837 --> 03:05:06,398
I was waiting to hear from our mayor.

2201
03:05:06,418 --> 03:05:07,038
She said nothing.

2202
03:05:07,438 --> 03:05:10,099
The new PR person, I didn't hear much.

2203
03:05:11,320 --> 03:05:13,121
Paulette van der Kloot did speak.

2204
03:05:13,901 --> 03:05:15,042
Thank you, Paulette van der Kloot.

2205
03:05:15,062 --> 03:05:15,602
That was good.

2206
03:05:16,522 --> 03:05:17,783
We need communication.

2207
03:05:18,643 --> 03:05:19,584
So I took videos.

2208
03:05:20,624 --> 03:05:20,944
I left.

2209
03:05:23,652 --> 03:05:34,538
What boggled my mind was that last Tuesday night, when we were almost censored, there were three officers of the law on the second floor of Medford City Hall, three officers of the law who didn't need to be there.

2210
03:05:34,838 --> 03:05:40,781
And then the next night, we talk about a bomb threat, but there was no security and no police officers.

2211
03:05:41,702 --> 03:05:47,325
There were people walking around, and I won't out anyone, but I asked, I said, where's the security?

2212
03:05:47,365 --> 03:05:48,265
And they laughed.

2213
03:05:48,846 --> 03:05:51,327
They laughed a condescending laugh, which I'm sure

2214
03:05:51,924 --> 03:05:58,149
Superintendent, it was aimed at you because there was no security and your own employees laughed when I brought it up.

2215
03:05:58,649 --> 03:05:59,550
This is disgraceful.

2216
03:05:59,630 --> 03:06:02,052
So, the superintendent wanted to reference me.

2217
03:06:03,654 --> 03:06:07,296
Here's my echoing what Mr. Capucci said.

2218
03:06:07,937 --> 03:06:09,538
Mr. Belson, you're too complacent.

2219
03:06:09,618 --> 03:06:10,279
It's time to go.

2220
03:06:10,999 --> 03:06:11,420
Thank you, sir.

2221
03:06:14,462 --> 03:06:15,263
Name and address of the record.

2222
03:06:15,607 --> 03:06:17,648
Hi, Cheryl Rodriguez, 281 Park Street.

2223
03:06:18,488 --> 03:06:19,969
I am a parent in the community.

2224
03:06:20,129 --> 03:06:22,850
I've had children in the school for 14 years.

2225
03:06:22,870 --> 03:06:36,455
I've gone through six principals, and I can attest that the notification system, if it does exist, is not known to these principals, because I've had six very different and unique experiences with notification.

2226
03:06:36,475 --> 03:06:38,196
I've been complaining about this for years.

2227
03:06:38,376 --> 03:06:41,717
So I was very excited to see Paul at Vanderclute put this resolution up.

2228
03:06:42,283 --> 03:06:46,726
And I hope that as parents we find out what the system is and it's implemented.

2229
03:06:47,346 --> 03:06:49,447
And maybe our PR person can help craft it.

2230
03:06:50,468 --> 03:06:50,788
Thanks.

2231
03:06:53,169 --> 03:06:59,153
On the motion that we send this to the superintendent for him to follow up and give us his answer by March.

2232
03:06:59,173 --> 03:07:00,494
All in favor?

2233
03:07:01,174 --> 03:07:01,294
Aye.

2234
03:07:01,534 --> 03:07:02,795
Roll call vote when requested.

2235
03:07:19,729 --> 03:07:24,231
Yes, and in the motion of 6-0, one absent, motion passes.

