03:07:41,416 --> 03:07:46,538
16-074 offered by Vice President of Council, Vice President Mungo Kern, be it resolved that the Methodist School Committee

2240
03:07:47,002 --> 03:07:57,911
and Memphis City Council to be provided a detailed report as to exactly which security cameras at Memphis High School are broken, along with an update of when they'll be fixed and replaced.

2241
03:07:58,051 --> 03:08:04,676
And I would ask also the same thing, if we could send this, but discuss this in executive session, Madam Vice President.

2242
03:08:06,698 --> 03:08:06,918
OK.

