2276
03:11:22,477 --> 03:11:24,538
So, that's 15 percent right there.

2277
03:11:25,779 --> 03:11:28,760
This was set at an open public meeting, Mr. President.

2278
03:11:28,780 --> 03:11:31,561
So, we're not talking about particulars.

2279
03:11:32,061 --> 03:11:34,382
But, really, that's a concern.

2280
03:11:34,943 --> 03:11:51,850
And it's a larger concern because in the call that I received, because I have two kids that attend the high school, was that 18 hours of tape was poured over to make sure that there was no hanky-panky going on the night before and days before.

2281
03:11:52,511 --> 03:11:54,692
And I would question the tape that they looked at.

2282
03:11:55,173 --> 03:11:58,975
I would question the fact that which cameras were working and weren't working.

2283
03:11:59,235 --> 03:12:02,857
So if you had a camera in the back of the building that wasn't working, they didn't look over that tape.

2284
03:12:02,997 --> 03:12:05,799
That tape just, you know, that didn't matter for security.

2285
03:12:06,119 --> 03:12:12,062
So there really is a concern here, Mr. President, outside of the lack of notification that we talked about.

2286
03:12:12,345 --> 03:12:20,414
It was mentioned the fact that even students, till today, I've asked both my kids, has there been any mention about what took place in the building?

2287
03:12:20,974 --> 03:12:21,975
These are young adults.

2288
03:12:22,656 --> 03:12:27,842
We're talking 15, 16, 17, 18 years old, and you don't tell them what took place in their building?

2289
03:12:28,643 --> 03:12:29,964
Shame on the administration.

2290
03:12:30,465 --> 03:12:31,706
Shame on them, Mr. President.

2291
03:12:32,952 --> 03:12:40,715
And another issue, Mr. President, part of the protocol, there's a number of steps that they can take when something like this happens.

2292
03:12:41,116 --> 03:12:45,597
One of them is a lockdown, one of them is a stand down, and one is evacuation.

2293
03:12:46,298 --> 03:12:53,081
The superintendent chose not to do evacuation, and that was after his insight into the issue.

2294
03:12:53,361 --> 03:12:55,782
He chose not to do a lockdown.

