Mrs. Puccio raised her four children, Anthony, Lorenzo, Maria, and Danny here in Medford.

2580
03:35:42,158 --> 03:35:42,919
Councilor Scott Petty.

2581
03:35:46,379 --> 03:35:47,680
Thank you, Mr. Mayor.

2582
03:35:47,700 --> 03:35:48,220
Mr. Puccio.

2583
03:35:50,698 --> 03:35:52,259
A very strong Meffitt family.

