2587
03:36:07,191 --> 03:36:08,392
If we could stand for a moment of silence.

2588
03:36:20,145 --> 03:36:20,525
Thank you.

2589
03:36:20,926 --> 03:36:21,506
I'll be brief.

2590
03:36:21,546 --> 03:36:26,688
I know it's late, but if we could get an update, maybe the clerk has some answers for us.

2591
03:36:26,728 --> 03:36:33,651
We had a meeting with MassDOT two weeks ago, and we had a number of resolutions that came out of that.

2592
03:36:33,911 --> 03:36:41,354
One, I know that Councilor Scarpelli, too, has been pushing for, is to have a point person in the city looking over the project.

2593
03:36:42,094 --> 03:36:44,875
So I was just wondering if the administration has...

2594
03:36:49,323 --> 03:36:50,144
I thought we had somebody.

2595
03:36:50,584 --> 03:36:50,864
No, I'm.

2596
03:36:51,625 --> 03:36:55,948
I'm afraid still didn't get to one person.

2597
03:36:55,988 --> 03:36:59,350
But I believe Mr. Carroll is still.

2598
03:37:00,211 --> 03:37:03,513
Yeah, the business owners haven't heard anything at that meeting.

2599
03:37:03,573 --> 03:37:10,458
We were told we could always reach out to OCD engineering or the building department.

2600
03:37:10,839 --> 03:37:17,964
But we asked specifically, is there going to be, we need one person to maybe go down once or twice a week, check it out, talk to the businesses.

2601
03:37:18,388 --> 03:37:32,036
have great communication with MassDOT, the council, and all parties involved, because obviously we have a long project ahead of us and a lot of problems that have taken place in the past.

2602
03:37:32,096 --> 03:37:37,399
And we would want to try to move forward on a day-to-day basis, knowing what's going on, when it's going on.

2603
03:37:39,020 --> 03:37:46,744
And we want to have a point person, not only that we can talk to, but that we can say to a business owner, call this person from OCD.

2604
03:37:46,824 --> 03:37:47,725
That's a point person.

2605
03:37:48,277 --> 03:37:52,021
She has direct contact with MassDOT on a daily basis.

2606
03:37:52,101 --> 03:37:53,482
She's walking by the area.

2607
03:37:53,582 --> 03:37:58,267
I mean, we've asked for that a number of times, and I think it's very important.

2608
03:37:58,347 --> 03:38:00,249
This project's going to be another year and a half.

2609
03:38:01,250 --> 03:38:06,395
We need a point person, not just somebody we can call and get a call back.

2610
03:38:06,435 --> 03:38:11,840
We know exactly who to contact to get answers to whatever's going on in the area.

2611
03:38:14,998 --> 03:38:21,460
It has been brought to my attention by the administration, Mr. President, that MassDOT will be putting in a crosswalk.

2612
03:38:21,560 --> 03:38:27,662
I've been led to believe that they were coming down to make a study if that can be done.

2613
03:38:27,742 --> 03:38:29,582
That determination has not been made yet.

2614
03:38:30,502 --> 03:38:33,383
Unless it's been made.

2615
03:38:34,223 --> 03:38:37,044
I've had discussions, but maybe we can get an update from the administration on that.

2616
03:38:37,064 --> 03:38:41,045
If we can get an update on the crosswalk on Main Street.

2617
03:38:48,125 --> 03:38:52,767
All in favor?

2618
